original: This is a quaint to-do list Penelope and Moxie gave me.
It's full of work leads, and there's plenty of room for me to erase and pencil in new plans.
Wow, there are a lot of options! Where should I begin?
This is the bag Moxie gave me. Well, she called it a 'satchel', I don't know what the difference is.
Pretty sure she made it herself.
It's certainly girly, but it should be able to carry a bunch of stuff.
